trans-unit.source: Contains values that specify the state of the content being loaded into a content element.
trans-unit.target: Contient des valeurs qui spécifient l’état du contenu en cours de chargement dans un élément de contenu.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that asynchronous loading of the content into the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element is beginning.
trans-unit.target: Spécifie que le chargement asynchrone du contenu dans l’élément [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] commence.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that asynchronous loading of the content into the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element is complete.
trans-unit.target: Spécifie que le chargement asynchrone du contenu dans l’élément [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] est terminé.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that asynchronous loading of the content into the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element is in progress.
trans-unit.target: Spécifie que le chargement asynchrone du contenu dans l’élément [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] est en cours.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation providers should specify the percent complete so that client applications will know how much more content remains.
trans-unit.target: Les fournisseurs UI Automation doivent spécifier que le pourcentage d’achèvement, pour que les applications clientes connaissent la quantité de contenu restante.
